125
00:11:50,060 --> 00:11:53,740
Now your dad's been reported for loan fraud.

126
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:56,660
We don't know where they've taken him.

127
00:11:57,420 --> 00:12:00,540
If the loan isn't repaid,
