203
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:42,580
- Come on.
- Stay calm.

204
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:44,020
- Drive safely.
- I know.

205
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:45,140
Drive safely.

206
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:46,976
Okay.

