00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:45,216
Jia Yu.

242
00:19:46,660 --> 00:19:48,576
Jia Yu.

243
00:19:51,648 --> 00:19:53,300
What happened to you?

244
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:55,700
You fought with someone?

245
00:19:55,700 --> 00:19:57,900
