266
00:21:42,540 --> 00:21:44,300
- Does it hurt?
- Yeah.

267
00:21:44,300 --> 00:21:46,380
Let me see.

268
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:47,540
If they hit you again,

269
00:21:47,540 --> 00:21:48,960
protect your face.

270
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:50,880
